2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can't%20trust%20such%20a%20big%20facility%2C%20who%20can%20we%20trust%3F%20Someone%20took%20his%20eye%20out%20in%20the%20ICU%20and%20the%20hospital%20is%20saying%20it%20doesn't%20know%20what%20has%20happened.%20This%20is%20very%20unfortunate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20officials%20said%20CCTV%20footage%20is%20being%20examined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20man's%20family%20has%20alleged%20that%20his%20eye%20has%20been%20taken%20out.%20It%20is%20clear%20the%20body%20has%20been%20tampered%20with.%20The%20doctors%20have%20said%20rats%20could%20have%20bitten%20off%20the%20eye%2C%20and%20we%20are%20investigating%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENMCH%20Medical%20Superintendent%20Dr%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Singh%20said%20rats%20could%20be%20responsible%20and%20that%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20is%20being%20conducted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFantus%20Kumar%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20ICU%20after%20suffering%20a%20firearm%20injury.%20He%20was%20operated%20upon%20and%20the%20bullet%20was%20removed%2C%20but%20he%20died%20at%208%3A55%20pm%20on%20Friday.%20His%20family%20was%20with%20him%20till%201%20am%20and%20they%20informed%20us%20at%205%20am%20that%20his%20left%20eye%20was%20missing.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20look%20into%20what%20has%20happened.%20An%20FIR%20has%20been%20filed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20possibility%20of%20rats%20biting%20off%20the%20eye%20cannot%20be%20ignored.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20a%20post-mortem.%20This%20is%20not%20acceptable%2C%20and%20anyone%20found%20guilty%20of%20negligence%20will%20be%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20also%20argued%20that%20removing%20an%20eye%2C%20which%20can%20only%20be%20used%20for%20a%20corneal%20transplant%2C%20won't%20make%20much%20sense%20in%20Kumar's%20case%20because%20he%20was%20dead%20for%20at%20least%20four%20hours%20before%20it%20went%20missing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20patient%20died%20at%208.55%20pm%20and%20the%20incident%20happened%20after%201.00%20am.%20The%20eye%2C%20even%20if%20someone%20took%20it%20out%2C%20won't%20be%20of%20much%20use.%20An%20eye%20can%20only%20be%20used%20if%20it%20is%20surgically%20removed%20within%20four%20to%20six%20hours%20of%20the%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731782820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fbcra07fo_bihae-eye-incident_625x300_17_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpatna-news%2Ffamily-claims-dead-mans-eye-taken-out-in-bihar-hospital-doctors-blame-rats-7036292%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20family%20of%20a%20man%20who%20died%20of%20a%20bullet%20injury%20while%20undergoing%20treatment%20in%20a%20Patna%20hospital%20was%20grieving%2C%20another%20shock%20awaited%20them%20-%20his%20left%20eye%20went%20missing%20hours%20after%20his%20death.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay%20Kumar%20shares%20UPDATE%20on%20'Hera%20Pheri%203'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731782802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115369123%2Cimgsize-39702.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshay-kumar-shares-update-on-hera-pheri-3-with-suniel-shetty-and-paresh-rawal-i-think-by-next-year-%2Farticleshow%2F115369123.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115369123.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20iconic%20comedy%20trio%20of%20Akshay%20Kumar%2C%20Paresh%20Rawal%2C%20and%20Sunil%20Shetty%20are%20set%20to%20reunite%20for%20Hera%20