ntent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20aim%20to%20ensure%20strict%20enforcement%20of%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20measures%20to%20control%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%2C%20a%20crucial%20review%20meeting%20was%20chaired%20on%20Saturday%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20a%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20chaired%20by%20Sujit%20Kumar%20Bajpayee%2C%20Member%2C%20of%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20it%20was%20highlighted%20that%20the%20upcoming%20winter%20season%20is%20a%20crucial%20period%20and%20thus%20the%20actions%20to%20be%20taken%20under%20different%20stages%20of%20GRAP%2C%20are%20to%20be%20implemented%20in%20true%20letter%20and%20spirit.%20The%20action%20taken%20reports%20received%20in%20the%20GRAP%20Monitoring%20Control%20Room%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20from%20different%20implementing%20authorities%20responsible%20for%20the%20abatement%20of%20air%20pollution%20in%20NCR%20States%2C%20was%20deliberated%20through%20a%20detailed%20presentation%2C%20inter-alia%20highlighting%20the%20following%20issues%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actions%20required%20to%20be%20taken%20under%20Stage%20III%20of%20GRAP%2C%20invoked%20since%20November%2015%20are%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20actions%20under%20Stage%20I%20and%20Stage%20II%2C%20which%20were%20invoked%20on%20October%2015%20and%20October%2022%20respectively.%20All%20implementing%20and%20enforcement%20agencies%20were%20advised%20to%20go%20through%20the%20revised%20GRAP%20guidelines%2C%20which%20are%20available%20on%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDaily%20reports%20on%20the%20action%20taken%20by%20NCR%20States%20are%20being%20generated%20and%20shared%20with%20Nodal%20Officers%20for%20corrective%20measures%20through%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%20of%20GRAP%20Monitoring%20Control%20Room%2C%20created%20for%20a%20smooth%20flow%20of%20information.%20The%20data%20is%20also%20being%20presented%20in%20different%20meetings%20with%20NCR%20States%20and%20the%20same%20was%20also%20highlighted%20in%20high-level%20meetings%20held%20recently%20with%20Govt.%20of%20Delhi%20on%20November%208%20and%20Govt.%20of%20Haryana%20on%20November%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActions%20to%20be%20taken%20in%20Stage%20III%20of%20GRAP%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20Stage%20I%20and%20Stage%20II%2C%20were%20also%20presented%20and%20explained%20in%20detail%20including%20banned%20and%20permitted%20Construction%20and%20Demolition%20(C%26amp%3BD)%20activities%20during%20Stage%20III%20of%20GRAP.%20With%20the%20invocation%20of%20Stage-III%20of%20GRAP%2C%20data%20on%20additional%20parameters%20under%20different%20sectors%20viz.%20Vehicular%2C%20C%26amp%3BD%2C%20Stone%20crusher%20and%20Mining%20needs%20to%20be%20submitted%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20as%20per%20shared%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20detailed%20presentation%2C%20inter-alia%2C%20the%20following%20issues%20were%20highlighted%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-compliance%20of%20dust%20control%20measures%20by%20C%26amp%3BD%20sites%20resulting%20in%20possible%20adverse%20impact%20on%20air%20quality%20in%20NCR%20must%20be%20dealt%20with%20strongly%20and%20all%20actions%20for%20levying%20Environmental%20Compensation%20(EC)%20and%20closure%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20such%20units%20till%20full%20compliance%20is%20achieved.%20Further%2C%20inspection%20for%20C%26amp%3BD%20sites%20must%20be%20intensified%20and%20actions%20for%20non-compliance%20are%20also%20required%20to%20be%20taken%20with%20a%20uniform%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20highlighted%20that%20with%20the%20invocation%20of%20Stage%20III%20of%20GRAP%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20numbers%20of%20Mechanical%20Road%20Sweeping%20Machines%20(MRSMs)%20are%20augmented%20without%20further%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effort%20for%20challenging%20the%20vehicle%20for%20non-possession%20of%20PUC%20and%20impounding%20End-of-Life%20(EoL)%20vehicles%20is%20also%20to%20be%20intensified%20further%20by%20traffic%20police%20and%20transport%20departments%20of%20NCR%20states%20considering%20their%20huge%20potential%20to%20deteriorate%20air%20quality%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20highlighted%20that%20the%20rate%20of%20resolution%20of%20complaints%20on%20different%20apps%2F%20X%20(Twitter)%20is%20not%20satisfactory.%20Further%2C%20concerned%20States%20must%20resolve%20the%20grievances%20within%20a%20week's%20time%20and%20tag%20CAQM%20while%20closing%20the%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20detailed%20discussions%2C%20inter-alia%2C%20the%20following%20action%20points%20were%20directed%20by%20Member%2C%20CAQM%20to%20concerned%20implementing%20authorities%20responsible%20for%20the%20abatement%20of%20air%20pollution%20in%20NCR%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20actions%20prescribed%20under%20GRAP%20need%20to%20be%20enforced%20strictly%20in%20true%20letter%20and%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20attention%20must%20be%20given%20to%20all%20identified%20hotspots%20in%20NCR%20states.%20GNCTD%20had%20already%20presented%20their%20action%20plan%20for%20identified%20hotspots%20in%20the%20high-level%20meeting%20held%20in%20Commission%20on%20November%208%20The%20same%20must%20be%20taken%20up%20on%20priority%2C%20except%20those%20actions%20which%20are%20prohibited%20under%20GRAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pending%20complaints%20from%20citizens%20on%20different%20Apps%20and%20Social%20Media%20till%20date%20must%20be%20resolved%20within%20a%20week.%20Further%2C%20CAQM%20must%20be%20tagged%20on%20social%20media%20while%20forwarding%20and%20resolving%20the%20complaints%20so%20that%20they%20are%20properly%20tracked%20and%20monitored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENodal%20officers%20for%20all%20agencies%20should%20coordinate%20actions%20in%20their%20respective%20agencies%20and%20concerned%20State%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(SPCB)%2F%20DPCC%20to%20also%20monitor%20the%20actions%20by%20different%20agencies%20besides%20action%20required%20by%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDaily%20reporting%20of%20actions%20under%20GRAP%20Stage-III%20must%20be%20provided%20in%20a%20shared%20format%20to%20the%20Commission%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20without%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20any%20clarification%20required%2C%20specific%20reference%20may%20be%20made%20to%20the%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20of%20concerned%20agencies%20shall%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20any%20laxity%20in%20the%20enforcement%20of%20the%20above%20directions%20and%20the%20same%20may%20attract%20action%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20CAQM%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731775920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frlcpup78_delhi-smog-_625x300_16_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fresolve-complaints-on-pollution-within-a-week-panel-to-delhi-other-states-7035767%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20an%20aim%20to%20ensure%20strict%20enforcement%20of%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20measures%20to%20control%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%2C%20a%20crucial%20review%20meeting%20was%20chaired%20on%20Saturday%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20a%20release%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akshay%20Kumar%20on%20why%20he%20took%20Canadian%20citizenship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731775353000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115366630%2Cimgsize-15254.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fakshay-kumar-reveals-why-