%20Wunderbar%20Films.%20The%20romantic%20comedy%20was%20written%20and%20directed%20by%20Nayanthara's%20husband%20and%20filmmaker%20Vignesh%20Shivan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fthis-is-an-all-time-low-nayanthara-reacts-to-dhanush-s-10-crore-copyright-lawsuit-over-netflix-documentary-7032659%5C%22%3ENayanthara%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0in%20the%20letter%20posted%20on%20her%20Instagram%20handle%2C%20claimed%20the%20team%20behind%20the%20documentary%20waited%20for%20Dhanush's%20approval%20for%20the%20release%20but%20%26quot%3Bfinally%20decided%20to%20give%20up%20and%20settled%20for%20the%20current%20version%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20%26quot%3Bdeclined%26quot%3B%20to%20permit%20the%20%26quot%3Busage%20of%20'Naanum%20Rowdy%20Dhaan'%20songs%20or%20visual%20cuts%20despite%20multiple%20requests%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BAn%20All-Time%20Low%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20mentioned%20that%20many%20%26quot%3Bindustry%20well-wishers%26quot%3B%20contributed%20to%20the%20Netflix%20documentary%20%26quot%3Babout%20me%2C%20my%20life%2C%20my%20love%2C%20and%20marriage%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sadly%20doesn't%20include%20the%20most%20special%20and%20important%20film%2C%20'Naanum%20Rowdy%20Dhaan'%2C%26quot%3B%20Nayanthara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhanush%20has%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20her%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20actor%20minced%20no%20words%20in%20criticising%20Dhanush%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Ball-time%20low%26quot%3B%20and%20asserted%20she%20would%20be%20giving%20a%20%26quot%3Bbefitting%26quot%3B%20reply%20to%20the%20notice%20through%20lawful%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20startled%20to%20read%20those%20lines%20wherein%20you%20questioned%20the%20usage%20of%20some%20videos%20(just%20three%20seconds)%20that%20were%20shot%20on%20our%20personal%20devices%2C%20and%20that%20too%20BTS%20visuals%20that%20are%20already%20very%20much%20publicly%20present%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20claimed%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%20as%20damages%20for%20the%20mere%20three%20seconds%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20all-time%20low%20from%20you%20and%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20your%20character.%20I%20wish%20you%20were%20half%20the%20person%20you%20portray%20on%20stage%20at%20audio%20launches%20in%20front%20of%20your%20innocent%20fans%2C%20but%20clearly%2C%20you%20do%20not%20practice%20what%20you%20preach%2C%20at%20least%20not%20with%20me%20and%20my%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENayanthara%20claimed%20that%20Dhanush%20said%20%26quot%3Bhorrible%20things%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20film%20that%20was%20released%20nearly%2010%20years%20ago%20and%20that%20he%20continues%20to%20act%20%26quot%3Bvile%20while%20wearing%20a%20mask%20in%20front%20of%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20learned%20through%20film%20circles%20that%20your%20ego%20was%20supremely%20hurt%20after%20the%20film%20became%20a%20blockbuster.%20Your%20displeasure%20over%20its%20success%20was%20perceptible%20even%20to%20the%20common%20man%20through%20award%20functions%20connected%20with%20this%20film%20(Filmfare%202016)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20Dhanush%20to%20watch%20the%20documentary%2C%20Nayanthara%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20%23SpreadLove%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20and%20pray%20that%20someday%20you%20are%20also%20fully%20capable%20of%20doing%20it%20and%20not%20just%20saying%20it%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fchange-and-find-happiness-vignesh-shivan-addresses-dhanush-s-10-crore-copyright-claim-over-netflix-documentary-7033554%5C%22%3EFilmmaker%20Shivan%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20stepped%20in%20to%20support%20his%20wife%2C%20sharing%20an%20old%20video%20of%20Dhanush%20on%20Instagram%2C%20where%20the%20actor%20spoke%20about%20positivity%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20living%20without%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20clip%2C%20taken%20from%20the%20audio%20launch%20of%20the%202017%20film%20Sakka%20Podu%20Podu%20Raja%2C%20shows%20Dhanush%20saying%20in%20Tamil%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20love%20we%20have%20for%20one%20should%20not%20turn%20into%20hate%20for%20another.%20If%20it%20changes%2C%20there%20is%20no%20meaning%20for%20that%20emotion.%20The%20world%20is%20going%20towards%20a%20pathetic%20condition.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20negativity.%20Nobody%20likes%20it%20if%20another%20person%20is%20doing%20good%20in%20life.%20Live%20and%20let%20live.%20Nobody%20should%20hate%20another%20person.%20If%20you%20like%20somebody%2C%20celebrate%20with%20them.%20If%20you%20don't%20like%20somebody%2C%20just%20move%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documentary%20is%20set%20to%20be%20released%20on%20November%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731774840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fu2queavo_nayanthara-dhanush_625x300_16_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnayanthara-dhanush-spat-rs-10-crore-lawsuit-open-letter-over-netflix-documentary-7035138%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20all-out%20war%20has%20broken%20out%20between%20south%20cinema%20superstars%20Nayanthara%20and%20Dhanush%20over%20a%20three-second%20clip%20in%20a%20Netflix%20documentary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnayanthara-dhanush-spat-rs-10-crore-lawsuit-open-letter-over-netflix-documentary-7035138%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20Haka%2C%20Traditional%20Maori%20Dance%20Performed%20By%20New%20Zealand%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand's%20youngest%20MP%2C%20Hana-Rawhiti%20Maipi-Clarke%2C%20on%20Thursday%20tore%20up%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20contentious%20Treaty%20Principles%20Bill%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-zealand-mp-hana-rawhiti-kareariki-maipi-clarke-leads-traditional-dance-rips-up-copy-of-bill-in-parliament-7020108%5C%22%3Eperformed%20a%20traditional%20Maori%20haka%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20House%20session.%20This%20bold%20move%20comes%20almost%20a%20year%20after%20she%20went%20viral%20for%20performing%20a%20haka%20during%20her%20maiden%20speech%20in%20parliament.%20The%2022-year-old%20Te%20Pati%20Maori%20MP%20interrupted%20the%20session%2C%20ripping%20apart%20the%20bill%20before%20breaking%20into%20the%20powerful%20dance.%20She%20was%20soon%20joined%20by%20others%20in%20the%20public%20gallery%2C%20prompting%20Speaker%20Gerry%20Brownlee%20to%20briefly%20suspend%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Maori%20Haka%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maori%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newzealand.com%2Fint%2Ffeature%2Fhaka%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3Ehaka%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20traditional%20performance%20that%20holds%20deep%20cultural%20significance%20for%20New%20Zealanders.%20It%20is%20known%20for%20its%20powerful%20energy%2C%20fierce%20facial%20expressions%20(pukana)%2C%20and%20physical%20movements%20like%20stamping%2C%20hand%20gestures%2C%20and%20chanting.%20The%20haka%20varies%20by%20region%2C%20with%20many%20telling%20stories%20of%20significant%20events%20in%20a%20tribe's%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrigins%20and%20significance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20haka's%20origins%20lie%20in%20Maori%20mythology%2C%20created%20by%20Tane-more%2C%20the%20son%20of%20the%20sun%20god%20and%20the%20summer%20maid.%20It%20symbolises%20vitality%20and%20energy%2C%20representing%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Maori%20people.%20Traditionally%2C%20the%20haka%20was%20performed%20for%20war%2C%20to%20celebrate%20achievements%2C%20or%20to%20welcome%20guests.%20Today%2C%20it%20is%20performed%20at%20important%20occasions%20like%20sporting%20events%2C%20weddings%2C%20and%20funerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETypes%20of%20Haka%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20various%20forms%20of%20haka%2C%20each%20with%20its%20unique%20purpose%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPeruperu%3A%20A%20war%20haka%20performed%20with%20weapons%20to%20show%20strength.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENgarahu%3A%20A%20semi-war%20dance%20performed%20to%20test%20warriors'%20readiness.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHaka%20Tui%20Waewae%3A%20A%20non-combative%20haka%20expressing%20emotions%20like%20joy%20or%20anger.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKa%20Mate%3A%20Created%20by%20Ngati%20Toa%20Chief%20Te%20Rauparaha%2C%20Ka%20Mate%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20his%20escape%20from%20capture%20and%20his%20subsequent%20rise%20as%20a%20great%20Maori%20leader.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20haka%20gained%20worldwide%20fame%20through%20New%20Zealand's%20All%20Blacks%20rugby%20team%2C%20who%20perform%20Ka%20Mate%20before%20each%20game.%20The%20performance%20is%20meant%20to%20assert%20dominance%2C%20energise%20the%20team%2C%20and%20honour%20Maori%20culture.%20This%20ritual%20has%20captivated%20audiences%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20experience%20haka%20firsthand%2C%20you%20can%20attend%20rugby%20matches%20or%20visit%20places%20like%20Rotorua%20where%20you%20can%20watch%20live%20performances%20or%20participate%20in%20traditional%20Maori%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731774360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F3jsgi91o_new-zealand-mp-haka_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-about-haka-traditional-maori-dance-performed-by-new-zealand-mp-7033755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20Zealand's%20youngest%20MP%2C%20Hana-Rawhiti%20Maipi-Clarke%2C%20on%20Thursday%20tore%20up%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20contentious%20Treaty%20Principles%20Bill%20and%20performed%20a%20traditional%20Maori%20haka%20during%20a%20House%20session.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22e