ide%20dishes.%20Enter%20a%20Crock-Pot%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslow-cooker-thanksgiving-ideas-2017-11%5C%22%3Eslow%20cooker%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlow%20cookers%20can%20help%20you%20make%20several%20easy%20Thanksgiving%20side%20dishes%2C%20from%20stuffing%20to%20cranberry%20sauce%20and%20delicious%20dips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%2015%20Thanksgiving%20sides%20you%20can%20make%20in%20a%20slow%20cooker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESweet-potato%20casserole%20with%20marshmallows%20can%20easily%20be%20made%20in%20a%20slow%20cooker.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222401%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sweet%20potatoes%20with%20cinnamon%20and%20marshmallows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fb2a6cd1c741f0019ac9f9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESweet%20potatoes%20with%20cinnamon%20and%20marshmallows.%3Cp%3ESara%20Seaberry%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESweet-potato%20casserole%20topped%20with%20marshmallows%20is%20a%20Thanksgiving%20favorite%2C%20and%20there%20are%20multiple%20recipes%20out%20there%20explaining%20how%20to%20make%20it%20in%20a%20slow%20cooker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20recipe%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdamndelicious.net%2F2016%2F11%2F21%2Fslow-cooker-sweet-potato-casserole%2F%5C%22%3EDamn%20Delicious%3C%2Fa%3E%20explains%20that%20the%20residual%20heat%20from%20the%20slow%20cooker%20is%20the%20perfect%20method%20for%20achieving%20gooey%2C%20melted%20marshmallows%20on%20top%20of%20your%20casserole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaking%20a%20side%20dish%20in%20a%20slow%20cooker%20saves%20room%20in%20the%20oven%20(which%20usually%20has%20the%20turkey%20or%20ham%20in%20it).%26quot%3B%20Sarah%20Olson%2C%20the%20blogger%20behind%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themagicalslowcooker.com%2Fabout-me%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Magical%20Slow%20Cooker%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20if%20you%20are%20traveling%20to%20another%20house%20for%20the%20holidays%2C%20the%20slow%20cooker%20will%20keep%20your%20dish%20warm%20at%20the%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMeatballs%20make%20a%20great%20appetizer%20for%20guests%20while%20you're%20busy%20cooking%20on%20the%20stove.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22meatballs%20in%20a%20slow%20cooker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fb2aac7402d49001924f20c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221950%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeatballs.%3Cp%3Eanewlifephotostudio%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20nothing%20worse%20than%20having%20hungry%20guests%20hanging%20around%20the%20kitchen%20waiting%20for%20dinner%20to%20be%20ready.%20Meatballs%20are%20the%20perfect%20appetizer%20for%20parties%20big%20and%20small%2C%20and%20they%20are%20easy%20to%20make%20in%20a%20slow%20cooker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlace%20your%20seasoned%2C%20raw%20meatballs%20into%20the%20slow%20cooker%2C%20top%20with%20sauce%2C%20and%20let%20the%20slow%20cooker%20finish%20them%20off%2C%20says%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spendwithpennies.com%2Fcrockpot-meatballs%2F%5C%22%3Erecipe%20by%20Spend%20With%20Pennies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20might%20be%20surprised%20to%20learn%20you%20can%20make%20mashed%20potatoes%20in%20a%20slow%20cooker.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22slow%20cooker%20mashed%20potatoes%20with%20wooden%20spoon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6197c2136f457d0018cd5a5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESlow%20cooker%20mashed%20potatoes.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMashed%20potatoes%20are%20a%20Thanksgiving%20staple%20%E2%80%94%20the%20meal%20s