r%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331419%2Fgujarat-bhargsetu-sharma-started-humans-with-humanity-animal-rescue-stray-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20rescue%2C%20treatment%2C%20and%20relief%20centre%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20place%20where%20sick%20and%20injured%20animals%20are%20treated%20and%20rehabilitated%20before%20being%20released%20back%20into%20their%20original%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%20with%20her%20morning%20walks%2C%20carrying%20bags%20of%20food%2C%20biscuits%20and%20medicines%20%E2%80%94%20feeding%20and%20treating%20every%20stray%20dog%20she%20encountered%20in%20the%20four-kilometre%20stretch%20between%20her%20residence%20and%20the%20Mayfair%20Tea%20Factory.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20see%20an%20injury%20or%20a%20sickness%2C%20I%20treat%20the%20animal%20on%20the%20spot.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20quick%20way%20to%20prevent%20the%20issue%20from%20becoming%20serious%20and%20expensive%20to%20treat%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20one%20of%20my%20morning%20walks%2C%20I%20was%20approached%20by%20a%20kind%20gentleman%2C%20who%2C%20on%20learning%20about%20what%20I%20do%2C%20offered%20me%20his%20space%20to%20open%20a%20relief%20centre%20free%20of%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20with%20a%20gratitude-filled%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20her%20on%20the%20street%2C%20I%20was%20out%20for%20my%20usual%20morning%20walk%20at%205%20am%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mani%20Chhetri%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20house.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20seen%20her%20many%20times%20before%2C%20helping%20every%20dog%20she%20came%20across.%20She%20would%20feed%20them%2C%20treat%20them%2C%20and%20do%20everything%20on%20her%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%20was%20thoroughly%20impressed%20by%20the%20compassion%20one%20woman%20could%20show%20and%20the%20resolve%20with%20which%20she%20continued%20her%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20any%20dog%20was%20sick%20or%20inj