5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20hurdles%20Aryan%20faced%20was%20sparking%20interest%20among%20students%20about%20the%20website.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20was%20the%20development%20of%20the%20platform%20itself.%20Aryan%20had%20limited%20experience%20with%20coding%20but%20made%20use%20of%20no-code%20platforms%20that%20allowed%20him%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20front-end%20design%20while%20his%20friends%20helped%20with%20the%20back-end%20coding.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learned%20a%20lot%20along%20the%20way.%20But%20my%20friends%20really%20helped%20me%20fine-tune%20the%20website%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20perfectionist%20tendencies%2C%20Aryan%20knew%20the%20importance%20of%20launching%20before%20everything%20was%20perfect.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20delayed%20the%20launch%20by%20a%20month%20because%20I%20wanted%20everything%20to%20look%20just%20right.%20But%20eventually%2C%20we%20had%20to%20launch%20and%20just%20work%20on%20improving%20things%20based%20on%20feedback%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20LaunchPad%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20he%20understood%20that%20gathering%20feedback%20from%20users%20was%20essential%20to%20improving%20the%20platform.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20parts%20of%20this%20journey%20has%20been%20hearing%20from%20students%20who%20say%20that%20LaunchPad%20is%20something%20they%E2%80%99ve%20never%20experienced%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aryan.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20learning%20skills%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20learned%20in%20school%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20keeps%20me%20motivated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERewarding%20impact%3A%20Students%E2%80%99%20success%20stories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunchPad%E2%80%99s%20approach%20is%20also%20highly%20personalised.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20course%20content%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href