%20to%20experience%20Rajasthani%20folk%20music%20live%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20unmistakable%20moment%20when%20your%20ears%20immediately%20perk%20up.%20This%20art%20form%20has%20been%20perfected%20over%20generations%2C%20so%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20tradition%20that%20it%20resonates%20through%20your%20very%20bones.%20It%20feels%20as%20if%20the%20artists%2C%20singing%20with%20heads%20held%20high%2C%20are%20not%20performing%20for%20the%20audience%2C%20but%20singing%20directly%20to%20a%20higher%20power%20in%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20only%20took%20one%20Shri%20Ravi%20Shankar%20%3Cem%3Eji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20extend%20the%20sitar%E2%80%99s%20influence%20for%20another%20century.%20Similarly%2C%20it%20will%20only%20take%20a%20few%20properly%20trained%20and%20passionate%20young%20people%20to%20revive%20the%20rich%20music%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20ensure%20its%20survival%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20assures%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Govind%20Singh%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20Genevive%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731072652000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D375518%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20world%20where%20traditional%20art%20forms%20are%20fading%20away%2C%20Govind%20Singh%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20Genevive%20are%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20revive%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20musical%20heritage.%20Through%20their%20one%20of%20a%20kind%20programme%2C%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20empowering%20young%20artists%20from%20folk%20communities%20to%20learn%20and%20celebrate%20their%20cultural%20identity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JEE%202025%20Now%20Allows%20Three%20Attempts%20%E2%80%93%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20Topper%E2%80%99s%20Guide%20To%20Make%20